{"id":290396,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/04/维权网-鞍山菁华小学多位家长堵路抗议向小学生/","date":"2013-04-24T06:30:44Z","modified":"2013-04-24T06:30:44Z","title":"维权网 | 鞍山菁华小学多位家长堵路抗议向小学生提供有毒食品（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>日</span><span>，辽宁省鞍山巿菁华小学多位学生家长堵路示威，抗议学校向小学生提供有毒食品。</span></p>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">28</span><span>日</span><span>中午，青华小学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>班的学生发现自己班的午饭里出现了许多银色的颗粒物，有学生认出这颗粒物是水银，于是告诉了班主任老师。老师派人从食堂里又拿来一盆饭，但是依旧有银色的颗粒物。老师自己掏钱买来了面包让同学们吃下。随后，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">300</span><span>余名鞍山市青华小学学生来沈阳市第九人民医院检查，其中少数学生被检测出“体内汞含量超标”的结果，最严重者尿汞含量超出参考值</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">40</span><span>倍。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>日</span><span>，学校向学生家长下发了《致家长的一封信》，信上写着：经过专家进行的详细调查，结论排除汞中毒，学生身体良好，无不良反应……个别学生尿汞少量超标，专家解释为生活环境、家庭饮食习惯等因素都可能造成体内尿汞超标。如偏爱食鱼类、水产品、化妆品等一般对身体无害。学校要求家长看完之后在这上面签字，家长表示绝对不能接受这个结论也不会签字的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">4</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日</span><span>，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">600</span><span>多家长都到教育局讨说法无果，当地政府再无人出面调查处理。有知情人透露，当地学校所供应大米均为教育局强制摊派。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-INYW60NHRB8/UXdHY8AC2UI/AAAAAAAAgy0/lEwPOlGcI8Q/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"297\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-INYW60NHRB8/UXdHY8AC2UI/AAAAAAAAgy0/lEwPOlGcI8Q/s400/1.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SdIOws6K6os/UXdHe8fDZrI/AAAAAAAAgzE/la_Wed17zO0/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-SdIOws6K6os/UXdHe8fDZrI/AAAAAAAAgzE/la_Wed17zO0/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"351\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0fbZFJTpuXQ/UXdHc51DndI/AAAAAAAAgy8/L0YD8IeCmPM/s1600/3.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"400\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-0fbZFJTpuXQ/UXdHc51DndI/AAAAAAAAgy8/L0YD8IeCmPM/s400/3.jpg\" width=\"328\" /></a></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}